# CRITICAL: Read Before Browser Actions

## Mastra Agent Chat (ALWAYS FOLLOW)

When testing agents in Mastra Studio:

1. **Agent CAN** type messages into the chat input field
2. **Agent CANNOT submit** - the browser automation cannot reliably click Send or press Enter, technical limitation
3. **ALWAYS ask user** to press Enter or click the Send button after typing a message in mastra agent chat
4. After user submits, wait and take a snapshot to see the agent's response

This applies to ALL agent testing sessions. Never attempt to submit messages automatically.
